<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wǔ kuài shí zi 迦南1123</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 xī shuǐ zhōng yǒu wǔ kuài guāng huá shí zi, zài jìng jìng děng dài.
 bù zhī hái yǒu duō shǎo tiān, hái yǒu duō shǎo zài.
 tīng jiàn liú shuǐ huā huā xiǎng, bù zhù de zàn měi shén.
 yǒu yī tiān shén yào yòng tā men, jī zhōng chóu dí de yào hài.
 wǔ kuài shí zi tóng xīn xiǎng, jīn tiān quán míng bái.
 fēng lì de léng jiǎo bù jiàn le, xiàn zài guāng huá qǐ lái.
 jīng guò shān hóng shā lì chōng jī, dōu shì shén de ān pái.
 chéng wèi xiǎo xiǎo de shí zi, cái néng zài xī zhōng děng dài.
 qí miào a, qí miào yǔ zhòu de dà zhǔ zǎi.
 wǒ men dōu yuàn yì bèi nǐ yòng, zài wú zì jǐ de xǐ ài.
 wǔ kuài xiǎo shí zi zhèng gǎn ēn, dà wèi yǐ zǒu guò lái.
 ná qǐ shí zi fàng zài náng zhōng qù yíng dí, wǒ men tóng shēng lái hē cǎi.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1123</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>